  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n<b>风华绝代上海滩</b><br/>\n<b>几束鲜花相对开</b><br/>\n<b>共匪兵压东巴黎</b><br/>\n<b>有人迟疑有人飞</b><br/>\n<b>城陷影残阴风摧</b><br/>\n<b>从此百色皆凋敝</b><br/>\n<b>冤魂怨骨曾经艳</b><br/>\n<b>胆识之别以命填</b>。<br/>\r\n—— 中华民族文化文艺百花齐放时代，一是春秋战国，一是民国亡于共匪前，呜呼。<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9SaHRSazFsLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/RhtRk1l.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/RhtRk1l.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RhtRk1l.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9TVnN4Tk1XLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/SVsxNMW.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/SVsxNMW.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SVsxNMW.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n <br/>\r\n为中共卖命下场凄惨难逃一死： <br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9JdjdnWWF5LmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/Iv7gYay.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Iv7gYay.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Iv7gYay.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n参看：<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/63160\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/63160\"><b>共产革命前后古巴妇女</b></a> </div>",
